806
00:39:09.160 --> 00:39:09.620
No.

807
00:39:09.780 --> 00:39:10.440
Do you have a card?

808
00:39:10.600 --> 00:39:11.600
Yeah.

809
00:39:12.560 --> 00:39:14.540
I'll be checking your socials.

810
00:39:25.020 --> 00:39:26.120
Where is she?

811
