00:45:06.000 --> 00:45:06.920
Angie. are you for real on this?

948
00:45:06.980 --> 00:45:09.440
Because. like. this would
really help me at the company.

949
00:45:09.620 --> 00:45:11.299
You better not be messing
with me on this. all right?

950
00:45:11.300 --> 00:45:12.560
