953
00:45:14.220 --> 00:45:14.720
We're going to the book party.

954
00:45:14.920 --> 00:45:15.100
Okay.

955
00:45:15.400 --> 00:45:18.080
Just. you know. please
keep this between us. okay?

956
00:45:18.180 --> 00:45:18.500
