980
00:46:04.480 --> 00:46:07.400
Okay. so. a weekend in the Hamptons.

981
00:46:07.660 --> 00:46:08.860
I mean. does this mean I'm in?

982
00:46:09.380 --> 00:46:09.880
No.

983
00:46:10.240 --> 00:46:11.320
