1023
00:47:28.820 --> 00:47:31.120
You have to present as
soon as we get them. okay?

1024
00:47:31.260 --> 00:47:32.260
Okay. Jen.

1025
00:47:32.360 --> 00:47:32.700
All right.

1026
00:47:33.100 --> 00:47:34.100
