1075
00:48:35.160 --> 00:48:36.180
Jenna Bush Hager.

1076
00:48:36.400 --> 00:48:36.600
Hi.

1077
00:48:36.600 --> 00:48:36.698
Hi.

1078
00:48:36.699 --> 00:48:36.800
Hi.

1079
00:48:36.840 --> 00:48:37.120
How are you?

1080
00:48:37.160 --> 00:48:38.180
Nice to meet you.

1081
00:48:38.200 --> 00:48:39.200
Nice to meet you.

