2097
01:35:44.250 --> 01:35:45.250
Okay.

2098
01:38:25.200 --> 01:38:33.200
Tonight. I'm here to talk about the
love affair between Runway and Italy.

2099
01:38:34.880 --> 01:38:41.914
And about Runway's continued pursuit
of the excellent. of the unparalleled.

2100
01:38:42.889 --> 01:38:48.560
in a world that we love so
much. the world of La Moda.

2101
01:39:03.160 --> 01:39:09.680
And tell me if this is a bit too much. but I was
thinking of the first issue that the cover girl could be.

2102
01:39:12.180 --> 01:39:15.640
