My God. do you work in a circus. Benji?

2105
01:39:19.980 --> 01:39:21.400
No. me. me.

2106
01:39:21.700 --> 01:39:24.440
Oh. that's brilliant.

2107
01:39:25.340 --> 01:39:25.780
Yes.

2108
01:39:25.940 --> 01:39:27.920
I know. because I'm a role model.

2109
